ğŸ” How Generative AI Works (High-Level Explanation)

Generative AI is mainly built using:

Large Language Models (LLMs)

Transformer architecture

Neural networks trained on massive datasets

It works by:

Understanding patterns in training data

Predicting the next word/token/pixel

Generating coherent and context-aware output

